00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:00,920
Rescue.

288
00:14:14,550 --> 00:14:15,390
Dad!

289
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:20,560
Dad!

290
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,320
Dad,

291
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:37,320
