and got into trouble,

299
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:13,080
would everything be different?

300
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:15,220
♪About holding you close♪

301
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:19,960
In your dream,

302
00:15:21,510 --> 00:15:25,010
