307
00:15:37,850 --> 00:15:38,690
However,

308
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:43,120
I have always wanted to know

309
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:47,670
when he looked at me for the last time,

310
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:50,870
