334
00:16:59,660 --> 00:17:00,980
♪Don't cry♪

335
00:17:02,030 --> 00:17:02,870
Really?

336
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:06,590
He didn't blame me?

337
00:17:07,870 --> 00:17:08,730
Of course.

338
00:17:08,730 --> 00:17:12,620
