351
00:17:38,820 --> 00:17:39,880
what would you do?

352
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:44,370
♪I've been saved♪

353
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:45,830
What can I do?

354
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,480
No matter what,

355
00:17:49,790 --> 00:17:51,400
